---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Terms — Protein Check"
  description="Terms of use for Protein Check. Estimates are AI-generated, approximate, and not medical advice."
  canonical="/terms"
>
  <main id="main" class="legal">
    <p class="back"><a href="/">← Protein Check</a></p>
    <h1>Terms of Use</h1>
    <p class="updated">Last updated June 2026</p>

    <div class="tldr">
      <strong>The short version:</strong> Protein Check gives you a free, AI-generated estimate of the
      protein and leucine in a meal photo. It's a helpful guide, not a measurement, and not medical or
      dietary advice. Use your judgment.
    </div>

    <h2>The service</h2>
    <p>Protein Check analyzes a meal photo and returns an estimate of total protein, total leucine, and
      a per-item breakdown. The service is provided free of charge and "as is," without warranties of
      any kind.</p>

    <h2>Estimates are approximate</h2>
    <p>Results are generated by an AI vision model and are estimates only. Real values depend on
      portion size, ingredients, and preparation that a photo cannot fully capture. Do not rely on
      Protein Check for medical, clinical, or therapeutic decisions. Consult a qualified professional
      for dietary or health guidance.</p>

    <h2>Acceptable use</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Upload only images you have the right to use.</li>
      <li>Don't attempt to disrupt, overload, or reverse-engineer the service.</li>
      <li>Don't use the service for any unlawful purpose.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Liability</h2>
    <p>To the fullest extent permitted by law, Protein Check and its creator are not liable for any
      damages arising from use of the service or reliance on its estimates.</p>

    <h2>Changes</h2>
    <p>These terms may be updated as the product evolves. Continued use means you accept the current
      version. Questions? Email <a href="mailto:raj@withmagic.ai">raj@withmagic.ai</a>.</p>
  </main>

  <style>
    .legal { max-width:680px; margin:0 auto; padding:40px 20px 8px; }
    .back a { font-weight:600; font-size:14px; text-decoration:none; }
    .legal h1 { font-size:clamp(30px,7vw,42px); margin:18px 0 4px; }
    .updated { color:var(--ink-muted); font-size:13px; margin:0 0 24px; }
    .tldr { background:var(--accent-soft); color:var(--accent-ink); border-radius:var(--radius); padding:16px 18px; font-size:15px; line-height:1.6; margin-bottom:8px; }
    .legal h2 { font-size:20px; margin:30px 0 8px; }
    .legal p, .legal li { color:var(--ink-soft); font-size:15.5px; }
    .legal ul { padding-left:20px; }
    .legal li { margin:6px 0; }
  </style>
</Layout>
